trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Gir dataene for den <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage"> </xref> hendelsen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs.MarginBounds%2A> property retrieves the rectangular area that represents the portion of the page between the margins.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs.MarginBounds%2A>egenskapen henter rektangulært område som representerer delen av siden mellom margene.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs.MarginBounds%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs.PageBounds%2A> property retrieves the rectangular area that represents the total area of the page.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs.PageBounds%2A>egenskapen henter rektangulært område som representerer det totale området på siden.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs.PageBounds%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs.Graphics%2A> property defines the graphics object with which to do the painting.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs.Graphics%2A>definerer grafikkobjekt som du kan gjøre malingen.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs.Graphics%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs.PageSettings%2A> property retrieves the printer settings for the current page.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs.PageSettings%2A>egenskapen henter skriverinnstillingene for gjeldende side.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintPageEventArgs.PageSettings%2A>

trans-unit.source: The remaining properties indicate whether a print job should be canceled or whether a print job has more pages.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapene gjenværende angi om en utskriftsjobben bør avbrytes, eller om et utskriftsjobben har flere sider.

trans-unit.source: For more information about printing with Windows Forms, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace overview.
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om utskrift med Windows Forms den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing>Oversikt over navneområde.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: If you wish to print from a Windows Presentation Foundation application, see the <xref:System.Printing> namespace.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du ønsker å skrive ut fra en Windows presentasjon Foundation-programmet, kan du se den <xref:System.Printing>navneområde.</xref:System.Printing>
